---
import EditorLayout from '../layouts/EditorLayout.astro';
import LineGutter from '../components/nvim/LineGutter.astro';
---

<EditorLayout title="About" description="About Dian Hanifudin Subhi">
  <LineGutter>
    <article class="prose">
      <h1>About</h1>

      <p>
        Hi, I'm <strong>Dian Hanifudin Subhi</strong> — a software engineer based in Indonesia.
        I build things with code, care deeply about developer experience, and spend too much time
        configuring my Neovim setup.
      </p>

      <h2>What I do</h2>
      <p>
        I work on web applications, tooling, and anything that sits at the intersection of
        engineering and design. My work spans backend systems, frontend interfaces, and the
        infrastructure that ties them together.
      </p>

      <h2>Tech I enjoy</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Languages: TypeScript, Go, Python, a touch of Rust</li>
        <li>Web: Astro, Vue, React — whatever fits the job</li>
        <li>Editor: Neovim (LazyVim config, Catppuccin Mocha, Fira Code)</li>
        <li>Infrastructure: containers, CI/CD, GitHub Actions</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>This site</h2>
      <p>
        Built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a> and
        styled to look like Neovim. The UI mimics Neo-tree, bufferline, lualine, which-key, and
        Telescope. Theme is Catppuccin (press <kbd>Space t</kbd> to toggle Latte ↔ Mocha).
      </p>
      <p>
        The site accepts contributions via GitHub issues using the OpenCode IssueOps workflow —
        see <a href="https://github.com/dhanifudin/dhanifudin.github.io/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md">CONTRIBUTING.md</a>
        for details.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/dhanifudin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@dhanifudin</a></li>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:dhanifudin@gmail.com">dhanifudin@gmail.com</a></li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </LineGutter>
</EditorLayout>
